&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Sounds interesting? Keep reading...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here’s what you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Grow and develop a world-class Commercial team by identifying, training, and implementing best practices that improve the team’s performance while maintaining culture and values&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive accountability for forecasting, pipeline, performance, enablement and attainment across your team&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Align and report on key metrics driving the revenue organization from new logo acquisition to revenue retention, pipeline build &amp;amp; conversion&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support continued refinement of the revenue and marketing organization’s defined playbooks, selling programs and initiatives&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Influence, collaborate and work with cross-functional leaders, departments; and teams to develop and execute successful strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with company policies and local, regional and federal regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach, grow and develop employees on a regular basis to build a dynamic sales organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and occasionally lead complex deal negotiations with your team&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support company diversity and inclusion initiatives, ensuring a diverse workplace to mirror our global customers and communities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support onboarding, enablement and employee growth strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
