&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years leadership management experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years sales leadership experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience in startup/scale-up environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in the SaaS industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience developing and retaining high-performing sales teams&lt;/li&gt;
