&lt;p&gt;Synack is committed to embracing diversity. Our people are our strength.&amp;nbsp; Each addition to our team is an opportunity to grow and diversify our ideas, experiences, and viewpoints. Synack strives to be inclusive of all people.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
