&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pricing, packaging &amp;amp; go-to-market&lt;/strong&gt; - Own the pricing and packaging for your portfolio, and lead the launch strategy and cross-functional execution that grow product adoption in the marketplace.&lt;/li&gt;
